Description_lang: Throw a trap at the target location that makes a path of thorny weeds up to $s1 yds long between where you threw the trap from and the targeted location. Trap will exist for up to $325869d. When an enemy approaches the trap, an area of bristleweed sprouts up for $325447d, dealing $325840s1 Nature damage every $325840t1 sec and snaring enemies by $325840s2%, stacking up to $325840u times. If this reaches $325840u stacks on an enemy, they are rooted for $325893d.
